my-claw/sdp/prd-artist-plan-completion.md:17:| APC-003 | Implement visitor identification by running face detection and embedding match against the observer camera frame at a configurable interval. | MUST | T2 | - Reads `/tmp/observer_frame.jpg` on schedule<br/>- Publishes identity result to `/tmp/visitor_identity.json`<br/>- Handles missing frame, no faces, and multiple faces gracefully |
