sdp/prd-cypherclaw-v2-2026-05-22.md:606:Every new module ships with unit tests in `tests/`. TDD is mandatory per durable instruction. Tests cover:
docs/codex-audio-investigation-brief.md:112:1. **Scarlett input reconnection** — the contact mics flowing into SC might be introducing noise/clicks. Test: disconnect inputs, listen for 5 min.
docs/codex-audio-investigation-brief.md:118:7. **The self-healing master chain** — `/s_new` with an existing node ID might cause a brief audio discontinuity even though scsynth "silently fails." Test: remove the `/s_new` and only keep `/n_set`.
