./sdp/verification/t-014@20260416t181925z-verify.md:55:1. **Proxy metrics**: GS, tempo ρ₁, and LZ76 return hardcoded values conditioned on `vel_sigma > 0`. When a real `partitura`-backed `PerformedPart` is fed in (non-dict score), `compute_metrics` falls through to `return {k: 0.0 for k in PASS_BANDS}` — all metrics become 0, which will fail every pass band. Wire up the real-audio path before any production render evaluation.
